            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Adjective</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><dl><dd><em>Also known as: 形容词 (xíngróngcí).</em></dd></dl>
<p>Adjectives are the "describing" words of a language. In Chinese, they have some characteristics that they don't have in English.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Adjective#Characteristics"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Characteristics</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="Adjective#Notes"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Notes</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="Adjective#Reduplication"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Reduplication</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-4"><a href="Adjective#Predicates"><span class="tocnumber">2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Predicates</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="Adjective#Special_adjectives_.E5.A4.9A_and_.E5.B0.91"><span class="tocnumber">2.3</span> <span class="toctext">Special adjectives 多 and 少</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-6"><a href="Adjective#Further_notes"><span class="tocnumber">2.4</span> <span class="toctext">Further notes</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
