<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-8"><a href="Adjective#Grammar_Patterns_for_Adjectives"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Grammar Patterns for Adjectives</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="Adjective#A2_Adjectives"><span class="tocnumber">4.1</span> <span class="toctext">A2 Adjectives</span></a></li>
